#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>concat()</code></strong>&nbsp;메서드는 매개변수로 전달된 모든 문자열을 호출 문자열에 붙인 새로운 문자열을 반환합니다.</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/string-concat.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"구문","title":"구문","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>str</var>.concat(<var>string2</var>, <var>string3</var>[, ..., <var>stringN</var>])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"매개변수","title":"매개변수","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"string2...stringn\"><code>string2...string<em>N</em></code></dt>\n <dd>합칠&nbsp;문자열.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"반환값","title":"반환값","isH3":true,"content":"<p>주어진 문자열을 모두 붙인 새로운 문자열.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"설명","title":"설명","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>concat()</code>&nbsp;함수는 호출 문자열에&nbsp;문자열 인수를&nbsp;이어 붙인 결과를 반환합니다. 원본 문자열과 결과 문자열의 변형은 서로에게 영향을 미치지 않습니다. 인수가&nbsp;문자열이 아니면 계산 전에 문자열로 변환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"concat_사용하기","title":"<code>concat()</code>&nbsp;사용하기","isH3":true,"content":"<p>아래 예제에서는&nbsp;문자열을 결합하여 새로운 문자열을 만듭니다.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>var hello = 'Hello, ';\nconsole.log(hello.concat('Kevin', '. Have a nice day.'));\n/* Hello, Kevin. Have a nice day. */\n\nvar greetList = ['Hello', ' ', 'Venkat', '!'];\n\"\".concat(...greetList); // \"Hello Venkat!\"\n\n\"\".concat({}); // [object Object]\n\"\".concat([]); // \"\"\n\"\".concat(null); // \"null\"\n\"\".concat(true); // \"true\"\n\"\".concat(4, 5); // \"45\"</code></pre>","titleAsText":"concat() 사용하기"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"성능","title":"성능","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>concat()</code>&nbsp;메서드보다&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators#assignment_operators\">할당 연산자 <small>(en-US)</small></a> (<code>+</code>, <code>+=</code>)를 사용하는게 더&nbsp;좋습니다. <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20170404182053/https://jsperf.com/concat-vs-plus-vs-join\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">성능 테스트</a>&nbsp;결과에 따르면 할당 연산자의 속도가 몇 배 빠릅니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"명세","title":"명세","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%203rd%20edition,%20December%201999.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'ECMAScript 3rd Edition (ECMA-262)' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 3rd Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition. Implemented in JavaScript 1.2.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.5.4.6\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'String.prototype.concat' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-string.prototype.concat\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'String.prot